cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a filter for segmenting the region of interest from lidar 3D point cloud for multirotor aerial vehicles, which is a problem related to robotics and computer vision. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions that the filter is used as a crucial component of fast obstacle avoidance system for agriculture drone operating at low altitude, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. Finally, since the filter is designed for real-time applications, it can also be related to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
